    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that everything feels so heavy. like i'm walking through sludge. people talk about \"finding peace\" or \"taking it step by step\" but that's just more work, right? more pretending. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the performance is to just... not be here. i feel like i'm just waiting for an exit that hasn't come yet.",
